#. <CLT 04>砂浜に着いた。<CLT>
msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Here we are at the rec room...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>どこまでも続く青い海、そして白い砂浜。<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>実に南国らしいロケーションだ。<CLT>
msgctxt "0002"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>There's all kinds of games and stuff to do in here.\n"
"Almost makes me feel like I'm not at school...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>俺たちの他に人影はないみたいだけど…<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>さてどうしようか？<CLT>
msgctxt "0003"
msgid "Wanna play Othello?"
msgstr ""

#. 泳ごう！
msgctxt "0004"
msgid "Sure, I'll play as long as you want."
msgstr ""

#. 応！
#. その言葉を待っておったぞ！
msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"But I'm a pretty tough opponent. I'm gonna use my\n"
"skills to predict your moves!"
msgstr ""

#. 安心せい！
#. ワシが立派な水泳選手に育ててやる！
msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"Anything I predict has a minimum 20% chance of\n"
"accuracy, all thanks to my intuition!"
msgstr ""

#. さあ、そうと決まれば特訓開始じゃあ！
msgctxt "0007"
msgid "Wait, or was it 30%...?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>後で誤解は解いておこう…<CLT>
msgctxt "0008"
msgid "Anyway...I can read your thoughts!"
msgstr ""

#. 焼こう！
msgctxt "0009"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I'm not sure he can even read his *own* thoughts...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. おお、たまにはそういうプレイも
#. いいかもしれんのう。
msgctxt "0010"
msgid "Let's play some pool."
msgstr ""

#. よし、オイル塗りがてらアレしてやるぞ！
msgctxt "0011"
msgid "Oh, but I've never played before."
msgstr ""

#. さあ、早く裸になって
#. そこに横たわるんじゃあ！
msgctxt "0012"
msgid ""
"Some say it lets you communicate with the universe.\n"
"Others, that it's a game inspired by the underworld..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>水着まで脱ぐ意味はないだろ…<CLT>
msgctxt "0013"
msgid ""
"They say it opens up a gateway into the kind of place\n"
"you'd never want to step foot."
msgstr ""

#. 砂の城を作ろう！
msgctxt "0014"
msgid "But...you think they're wrong about that?"
msgstr ""

#. ふぅむ…集中力を鍛えるのに
#. もしかしたら役立つかもしれんが…
msgctxt "0015"
msgid "Okay! Then teach me how to play!"
msgstr ""

#. お前さんの場合、まずはとにかく
#. 筋肉を作る事を優先すべきじゃぞ？
msgctxt "0016"
msgid "Let's give darts a shot."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>別に何かの特訓とかじゃないんだけどな…<CLT>
msgctxt "0017"
msgid "What are you gonna do with those darts!?"
msgstr ""

#. とりあえず走ろうか
msgctxt "0018"
msgid ""
"...Oh, sorry. Seeing those darts just reminded me of\n"
"something from my past."
msgstr ""

#. おお、砂浜でランニングか！
#. ワシの好きなシチュエーションじゃあ！
msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"Ya see, one time an assassin tried to kill me using a\n"
"blowgun..."
msgstr ""

#. これで夕日か朝日がバックにあれば
#. 最高なんじゃが…
msgctxt "0020"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>How could that possibly have happened...?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. ま、その時間まで走り続ければ
#. いいだけの話じゃな！
msgctxt "0021"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like nobody's here right now.\n"
"What should we do?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. よぉし、ではさっそく始めるとするぞぉぉ！
msgctxt "0022"
msgid "Let's check our horoscope in the magazine."
msgstr ""

#. とりあえず埋まろうか
msgctxt "0023"
msgid ""
"Oh yeah, people keep telling me I should get into that\n"
"kind of thing."
msgstr ""

#. 埋まるというのは…この砂にか？
#. むぅ…ワシの知らん特訓法じゃな。
msgctxt "0024"
msgid ""
"But if you serialize it, the pay is crap. That's not\n"
"where the real money is."
msgstr ""

#. よし、日向。
#. ちょっとワシに実践して見せてくれ。
msgctxt "0025"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Why are you telling me that...?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. …で、ワシが埋まるのか？
#. それともお前さんを埋めればいいのか？
msgctxt "0026"
msgid "They even have magazines on the occult."
msgstr ""

#. しかし砂に埋められても窒息せんとは…
#. お前さんの鍛えっぷりには、さすがのワシも驚いたぞ…
msgctxt "0027"
msgid "It's not occult!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>いや、そういうんじゃないから…<CLT>
msgctxt "0028"
msgid ""
"This here is a serious research journal. Show some\n"
"respect!"
msgstr ""

#. とりあえず脱ごうか
msgctxt "0029"
msgid "Is that a slot machine back there...?"
msgstr ""

#. なんと積極的…いや、せっかち過ぎるわ！
msgctxt "0030"
msgid "Hmm... The time has come."
msgstr ""

#. 何はともあれまずは準備体操じゃろうが！
#. さあ、とっとと始めるぞ！
msgctxt "0031"
msgid "As men, it's time we took that one big risk."
msgstr ""

#. スイカを割ろう
msgctxt "0032"
msgid ""
"But with my fortune-telling by my side,\n"
"I'm ready for it..."
msgstr ""

#. おお！
#. それはなかなか色々鍛えられそうじゃの！
msgctxt "0033"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like nobody's here right now.\n"
"What should we do?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. 目隠しによって研ぎ澄まされた五感が
#. 新たな感覚の扉を開く…
msgctxt "0034"
msgid "Kinda boring here, huh...?"
msgstr ""

#. 奥義の伝授には欠かせない特訓法じゃな！
msgctxt "0035"
msgid "There's plenty of stuff to keep yourself occupied!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>奥義って何のだ…<CLT>
msgctxt "0036"
msgid ""
"You just don't have the proper ambition!\n"
"You need to wake up, Makoto!"
msgstr ""

#. 椰子の実を落とそう
msgctxt "0037"
msgid "I'm not sure about any of these games..."
msgstr ""

#. おお、そいつは南国ならではの特訓法じゃな！
msgctxt "0038"
msgid ""
"Then all that's left is to flip through these\n"
"magazines."
msgstr ""

#. あらゆる攻撃によって木を揺らし、
#. それでもダメなら速やかに登り実を刈り取る…
msgctxt "0039"
msgid "So...let's see if we can find any dirty fold-outs!"
msgstr ""

#. 実に実践的なトレーニングになるのう！
msgctxt "0040"
msgid "Oh, but not for you, Makoto! You're too young!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>何のトレーニングかはよくわからないけどな…<CLT>
msgctxt "0041"
msgid "Hope's Peak really is amazing..."
msgstr ""

#. 棒倒しでもするか
msgctxt "0042"
msgid ""
"Yeah, seriously. With a room like this? It's totally\n"
"outta this world..."
msgstr ""

#. 懐かしいのう…
#. 幼い頃、よく１人でやったもんじゃ…
msgctxt "0043"
msgid ""
"Which means the school could totally put together a\n"
"crazy event like what's going on right now!"
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0044"
msgid ""
"I sure wish they'd show up and tell us how they pulled\n"
"it all off..."
msgstr ""

#. むう、いかんいかん！
#. つい感傷に浸ってしまったわ！
msgctxt "0045"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like nobody's here right now.\n"
"What should we do?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
